		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />No. I mean registers $D00x (except $D001) enable nametable control (NC). This game (MKII and variants) ignore NC, only $D001 mirroring control should work. Other games (Samurai Spirits?) break if you disable $D00x.

		

		</td>
